## Description {#details}

This <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sdnode">SDNode</a> is used for PSEUDO&#95;PROBE values, which are the function guid and the index of the basic block being probed.

A pseudo probe serves as a place holder and will be removed at the end of compilation. It does not have any operand because we do not want the instruction selection to deal with any.
